{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a003", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 3, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The EX dataset shows the unblinded administrations.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a004", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 4, "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 7", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 7, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a005", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 5, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The study in this example involved weekly infusions of drug Z 10 mg/kg.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a006", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 6, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If a subject experienced a dose-limiting toxicity (DLT), the intended dose could be reduced to 7.5 mg/kg.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a007", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 7, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The example CRF below was for subject ABC123-0201, who weighed 55 kg.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a008", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 8, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The CRF shows that:", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a009", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 9, "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "The subject's first administration of drug Z was on 2009-02-13; the intended dose was 10 mg/kg, but the actual amount given was 99 mL at 5.5 mL/mL, so the actual dose was 9.9 mg/kg.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a010", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 10, "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "The subject's second administration of drug Z occurred on 2009-02-20; the intended dose was reduced to 7.5 mg/kg due to dose-limiting toxicity, and the infusion was stopped early due to an injection site reaction.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a011", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 11, "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "However, the actual amount given was 35 mL at a concentration of 4.12 mg/mL, so the calculated actual dose was 2.6 mg/kg.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0117_a012", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 117, "atom_index_on_page": 12, "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "The subject's third administration was intended to occur on 2009-02-27; the intended dose was 7.5 mg/kg but, due to a personal reason, the administration did not occur.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
